      <title>韩国发生火灾 梅赛德斯、宝马公布电动汽车电池制造商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/mercedes-bmw-reveal-ev-battery-makers-amid-fire-fears-in-korea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在韩国发生电动汽车爆炸事件并引发全国性安全调查后，梅赛德斯奔驰集团和宝马集团的韩国子公司首次披露了为其供应电动汽车电池的公司名称。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/mercedes-bmw-reveal-ev-battery-makers-amid-fire-fears-in-korea</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 06:12:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国失业率意外下降 表明经济强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/uk-unemployment-dips-unexpectedly-but-growth-in-wages-slows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国失业率在企业加大招聘力度后意外下降，这表明英国经济潜在实力强劲，这给英国央行降低利率的举措带来复杂性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/uk-unemployment-dips-unexpectedly-but-growth-in-wages-slows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 06:11:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
